{"article_id":"0exgDfZnemsf31lS","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The White House said Sunday","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"it can not rule out another government shutdown","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"as it gets mixed signals from Democrats and Republicans","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"racing a Friday deadline","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"to fund President Trump ' s border-wall demands","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"and keep federal operations humming .","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"White House Chief of Staff Mick Mulvaney said","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"proposed funding is all over the map","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"and that Democrats ' are pushing to cap the number of detainee beds for people","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"who cross into the U.S. illegally ,","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"causing talks to stall .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"\" The government shutdown is still on the table .","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"We do not want it to come to that ,","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"but that option is still open to the president","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"and will remain so , \"","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"White House Chief of Staff Mick Mulvaney told Fox News Sunday .","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"Mr. Trump ,","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"whose demands for wall money led to a monthlong shutdown ,","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"said","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"Democrats must shoulder blame","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"if funding lapses again .","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"He said","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"they ' re not offering anything near the $ 5.7-billion","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"he says","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"is needed for his barrier with Mexico ,","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"while raising unnecessary hurdles .","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"\" They are offering very little money for the desperately needed Border Wall","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"& now , out of the blue , want a cap on convicted violent felons to be held in detention ! \"","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"he tweeted Sunday .","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"Senate Appropriations Committee Chairman Richard Shelby and Sen. Jon Tester , Montana Democrat , said","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"things could still work out","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"- or be a \" train wreck . \"","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"\" I ' ll say","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"50-50 we get a deal , \"","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"Mr. Shelby told Fox .","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"House Budget Committee Chairman John Yarmuth and Rep. Tom Graves , Georgia Republican , were more optimistic ,","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"telling ABC ' s \" This Week \"","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"they can still craft a bill","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"that will make it through both chambers .","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"Mr. Mulvaney said","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"Mr. Trump will wait for Congress ' offer","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"and then figure out how to cobble together the funds","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"he needs","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"to build the wall","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"he promised voters in 2016 .","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"\" This is going to get built with or without Congress , \"","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"said Mr. Mulvaney ,","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"who is serving in an interim capacity .","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"Mr. Trump has floated the idea","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"of going it alone","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"by declaring an emergency at the southern border","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"to build the wall .","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"Congressional Republicans are skittish about that idea ,","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"it would set a broad precedent for presidential powers .","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"Mr. Mulvaney said","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"Mr. Trump also might also search the couch cushions for federal dollars","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"and reprogram them toward the wall .","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"The simmering fight over the wall sparked a government shutdown from Dec. 22 to Jan. 25","depth":4},{"id":59,"text":"- the longest in history .","depth":4},{"id":60,"text":"Congress passed a stopgap bill","depth":5},{"id":61,"text":"to reopen the government","depth":6},{"id":62,"text":"and force talks over border security ,","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"though federal workers could be furloughed again","depth":5},{"id":64,"text":"if talks fail .","depth":5},{"id":65,"text":"\" I ' m hoping","depth":4},{"id":66,"text":"we can get off the dime later today or in the morning , \"","depth":4},{"id":67,"text":"Mr. Shelby said .","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":135,"left":125,"right":134,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":125,"left":83,"right":124,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":83,"left":73,"right":82,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":73,"left":69,"right":72,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":69,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":72,"left":2,"right":71,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":71,"left":3,"right":70,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":70,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":82,"left":77,"right":81,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":77,"left":6,"right":76,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":76,"left":7,"right":75,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":75,"left":74,"right":10,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":74,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":81,"left":11,"right":80,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":80,"left":79,"right":15,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":79,"left":12,"right":78,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":78,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":124,"left":105,"right":123,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"